  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569980/extras/07c1cf08a6133ff1c9d2982156b44b19.avif?t=1742368684\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569980/extras_big/07c1cf08a6133ff1c9d2982156b44b19.avif?t=1742368684 width=800 height=145 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are <strong>7 different games</strong> inspired by cult horror movies from the 80's and 90's. That exaggerated horror in some cases even comical and disturbing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some games are more horror and tension oriented, others are based on bullshit movies like (Scary Movie).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Each game has its own particularity, making them unique! Embark on various adventures and take a dive back to the 80s.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What games come in this collection?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>1873</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569980/extras/85b38f134e82ab75c14131f409d1dcd2.poster.avif?t=1742368684\" width=590 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569980/extras/85b38f134e82ab75c14131f409d1dcd2.webm?t=1742368684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"1873\"</strong> is a horror and investigation game, with elements of armed combat. Using the vibe of the 1800s. For those who are used to my games, this one has a very different style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DAD</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569980/extras/be92e2f0c608c8b1ff0b51de855e53cb.avif?t=1742368684\" width=590 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"DAD\"</strong> is a horror game with a bizarre style and story. Inspired by horror and suspense films from the 80s and 90s. With PS1 style graphics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fart Killer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569980/extras/040b00f94f4195ffcb0fbe6137e4222c.poster.avif?t=1742368684\" width=590 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569980/extras/040b00f94f4195ffcb0fbe6137e4222c.webm?t=1742368684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569980/extras/040b00f94f4195ffcb0fbe6137e4222c.mp4?t=1742368684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Fart Killer\"</strong> is a short trash comedy game mixed with cult horror from the 80s. With totally absurd and meaningless scenes. Don't expect a super Hollywood production... It's much better than that!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gears 2</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569980/extras/8c6a1a31b7dec07a7ba3e1c799fa4786.poster.avif?t=1742368684\" width=590 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569980/extras/8c6a1a31b7dec07a7ba3e1c799fa4786.webm?t=1742368684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569980/extras/8c6a1a31b7dec07a7ba3e1c799fa4786.mp4?t=1742368684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Gears 2\"</strong> is a psychological survival horror game. Inspired by the movies \"SAW\". Bringing different mechanics from the first game. Bringing tense moments with a lot of gore... forcing you to make decisions that will lead to life or death.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Halloween Revenge</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569980/extras/66a64ba957e44e76d9aca0d28c218d69.poster.avif?t=1742368684\" width=590 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569980/extras/66a64ba957e44e76d9aca0d28c218d69.webm?t=1742368684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569980/extras/66a64ba957e44e76d9aca0d28c218d69.mp4?t=1742368684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Halloween Revenge\"</strong> is a short horror game inspired by trash horror movies from the 80s. Mixing weird horror with comedy and weird characters. This mix results in a nostalgic game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Trash Night</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569980/extras/1851b5360adff0039a4d19b66e15d2db.poster.avif?t=1742368684\" width=590 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569980/extras/1851b5360adff0039a4d19b66e15d2db.webm?t=1742368684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569980/extras/1851b5360adff0039a4d19b66e15d2db.mp4?t=1742368684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Trash Night\"</strong> is a horror and drama game inspired by the cult horror films of the 80s and 90s... The golden age of VHS tapes. With \"PS1\" style graphics and an environment reminiscent of low-budget films.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>We Are not Alone - Contact</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569980/extras/2cb72caed6bcda88804217500c3fd78f.poster.avif?t=1742368684\" width=590 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569980/extras/2cb72caed6bcda88804217500c3fd78f.webm?t=1742368684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569980/extras/2cb72caed6bcda88804217500c3fd78f.mp4?t=1742368684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"We Are Not Alone - Contact\"</strong> is a reimagining of the first game. Inspired by alien horror films from the 80s, bringing comical horror and at the same time scary and bloody.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569980/extras/f97af891e00da7f7590fba0abe2e319f.avif?t=1742368684\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3569980/extras_big/f97af891e00da7f7590fba0abe2e319f.avif?t=1742368684 width=800 height=145 /></span></p>",
